{{Infobox dot-com company | name = Voot | logo = Voot website logo.png | owner = [[Viacom 18]] | area_served = India | location_city = Mumbai, India | url = {{url|http://www.voot.com}} | website_type = [[Entertainment]], [[video streaming]], [[video on demand]], [[web portal]] | launch_date = March 2016 | registration = Optional | alexa = {{DecreasePositive}} 1,431 (June 2018)<ref>https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/voot.com</ref> | language = English, Hindi, Kannada, Gujarati, Marathi, Bengali,Tamil }}
'''Voot''', launched, forms the digital arm of [[Viacom 18]]. It is Viacom18's advertising-led video-on-demand platform<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/media/entertainment/media/viacom18-launches-video-on-demand-platform-voot/articleshow/51606120.cms|title=Viacom18 launches video-on-demand platform Voot - The Economic Times|newspaper=The Economic Times|access-date=2016-11-07}}</ref> that is available as an app for [[iOS]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/in/app/voot-tv-shows-movies-cartoons/id1011777157?mt=8|title=Voot – TV Shows, Movies & Cartoons on the App Store|website=App Store|access-date=2016-11-07}}</ref> and [[Android (operating system)|Android]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tv.v18.viola&hl=en|title=Voot TV Shows Movies Cartoons - Android Apps on Google Play|last=|first=|access-date=November 1, 2017|website=play.google.com|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=}}</ref> users, and a website for desktop consumption.
Voot is available only in [[India]], and hosts over 40,000 hours of video content<ref name=":1" /> that includes shows from channels like [[MTV India|MTV]], [[Nickelodeon India|Nickelodeon]] and [[Colors TV|Colors]].<ref name=":0" /> Content is also available in multiple languages like Kannada, Marathi, Bengali, Gujarati and Tamil.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.firstpost.com/entertainment/from-voot-to-viu-sun-nxt-to-hoichoi-ott-platforms-are-offering-a-bounty-of-regional-content-4187227.html|title=Firstpost - Voot in Regional Languages|last=|first=|date=|work=|access-date=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=}}</ref>
==Programming== Voot has content from [[Colors TV]], [[MTV India]], [[Nickelodeon India]] and other [[Viacom 18]] owned television channels. It also hosts many [[Bollywood]] films for streaming.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/viacom18-launches-video-on-demand-platform-voot_6055981.html|title=Viacom18 launches video-on-demand platform Voot|website=www.moneycontrol.com|access-date=2016-11-07}}</ref> It has produced several 'Voot Original' shows for streaming as well. In the children’s segment, it is working on shows in Malayalam and Telugu.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.livemint.com/Opinion/JUouupMyF9AzfUN1Vw7NNJ/Digital-platforms-mainstream-regional-content.html|title=LiveMint - Voot Offers Regional Content|last=|first=|date=|work=|access-date=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=}}</ref>
